to hire a new donut boy.

134
00:06:05,610 --> 00:06:08,810
[Crowd booing]
No!

135
00:06:08,850 --> 00:06:12,420
You've got to be kidding me!

136
00:06:12,450 --> 00:06:15,790
How did this get
on the Internet so fast?

137
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:18,660
